original_title: Tori Amos - Video Collection: Fade to Red
overview: This collection looks at the unique and compelling videos (1991-2005) that illustrate Tori Amos' musical vision. Includes: 'Past the Mission', 'Jackie's Strength', 'Winter', 'Cornflake Girl', '1000 Oceans', 'Bliss', 'Talula', 'Pretty Good Year' and many more.
title: Tori Amos - Video Collection: Fade to Red
